Description: In a multi-tab dialog, switch tabs
Open a search field in a dialog with a list
expand all children and subchildren of the currently selected element
expand direct children of the currently selected element
select the topmost/lowermost visible element in the list
select the previous/next visible element in the list
select element on previous/next page of list
Jump to the first editable filed

Keys: ctrl+up or ctrl+down or ctrl+right or ctrl+left
Keys (macOS): cmd+up or cmd+down or cmd+right or cmd+left

Description: Toggle guides and snapping to guides
Toggle grids and snapping to grids
resize page to current selection, or to the drawing if nothing is selected
Set brush width to its minimum or maximum
